parameters:
Orca Asparagus-Mayor: To think you'd come back after being
beaten so badly... Well, it doesn't matter, I'll just crush
you again!! Without your monster suit comrades, can you
really fight the same as before!?

Memimi: You wouldn't understand... The power of everyone now
resides within my heart!! The strength of a monster isn't
determined by a monster suit!!

Memimi: After all, isn't that just a urethane costume?! How
could you become stronger just by slapping together such a
hodgepodge?! It's all about spirit, the spirit!!!
Orca Asparagus-Mayor: You shouldn't say that, damn you!!!

Orca Asparagus-Mayor: Just give up already... You can't beat
me, and every time you lose, you just get messed up even
more. Give up on everything and join me, along with that
shark bastard...

Memimi: No matter what happens to me, I will never accept
those terms!! Even if I were to be violated by hundreds of
men in the middle of the street, my butt hole ravaged, and
even if that footage with my real name and school name
uncensored were to be spread on the net!!

Defeated by the mayor, Memimi suffered intense
humiliation...
